      "instruction": "<p>Once the orzo is almost cooked, heat a separate, large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> king prawns</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until cooked through</p>",
