      "instruction": "<p>Season the orzo with a generous grind of <strong>pepper</strong> and squeeze in the <strong>juice</strong> of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong></p><p>Taste for seasoning, adding more <strong>salt</strong> if needed – this is your<strong> red pepper & saffron orzo</strong></p>",
